Ftrump-aims-cut-taxes-tips-gen-zers-waiters-who-gains-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20taxes%20on%20tips%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftax-tips-overtime-trump-proposals-income-money-election-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eovertime%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmedicaid-trump-republicans-house-budget-social-security-medicare-musk-doge-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecuts%20to%20Medicaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BMAGA%20accounts%26quot%3B%20for%20children%20and%20several%20other%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20take%20weeks%20for%20lawmakers%20in%20the%20House%20and%20Senate%20to%20work%20out%20the%20final%20details%2C%20and%20it's%20likely%20that%20some%20changes%20will%20be%20made%20along%20the%20way.%20Republicans%20hope%20to%20send%20the%20bill%20to%20Trump's%20desk%20by%20July%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20you%20should%20know%20about%20what's%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BOne%20Big%20Beautiful%20Bill.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ae2c5afb-c1d7-4932-849c-86bac4d69a7d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20bill%20includes%20cuts%20to%20Medicaid%2C%20and%20millions%20could%20lose%20health%20coverage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20plan%20approved%20by%20the%20House%20Energy%20and%20Commerce%20Committee%2C%20states%20would%20implement%20work%20requirements%20in%202029%20for%20childless%20adults%20on%20Medicaid%20who%20do%20not%20have%20a%20disability%2C%20mandating%20they%20work%20for%2080%20hours%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20component%20of%20the%20plan%20would%20increase%20the%20price%20of%20doctors'%20visits%2C%20mandating%20beneficiaries%20making%20above%20the%20federal%20poverty%20limit%20to%20pay%20co-payments%20of%20up%20to%20%2435.%20States%20would%20also%20be%20required%20to%20stop%20taxing%20hospitals%20and%20nursing%20homes%20in%20order%20to%20secure%20more%20federal%20funding.%3C%2F