4%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBearaby%20(left)%20and%20Silk%20%26amp%3B%20Snow's%20(right)%20weighted%20blankets%20are%20visually%20very%20similar%2C%20but%20don't%20be%20fooled.%20There's%20a%20distinct%20difference%20in%20their%20design.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20testing%20these%20two%20weighted%20blankets%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%20the%20fabric%20of%20the%20Silk%20%26amp%3B%20Snow%20blanket%20had%20a%20looser%2C%20more%20distressed%20weave.%20The%20fabric%20itself%20is%20also%20looser%2C%20so%20it%20has%20a%20relaxed%20look%20and%20feel.%20I%20noticed%20that%20this%20loose%20knit%20also%20means%20the%20loops%20are%20prone%20to%20stretching%20out%20during%20use.%20It's%20also%20altogether%20chunkier%20than%20the%20Bearaby%20blanket.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Bearaby's%20Cotton%20Napper%20has%20a%20tighter%20knit%20with%20a%20plump%20cotton%20fabric.%20When%20placing%20the%20two%20blankets%20side%20by%20side%2C%20there's%20an%20obvious%20difference%20between%20the%20designs%20of%20the%20fabric.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Silk%20%26amp%3B%20Snow%20Knitted%20Weighted%20Blanket%20skews%20larger%20than%20Bearaby's%20Cotton%20Napper.%20Even%20when%20the%20weights%20are%20the%20same%2C%20the%20Silk%20%26amp%3B%20Snow%20blanket%20is%20one%20to%20eight%20inches%20longer%20and%20wider%20than%20the%20Bearaby%20blanket.%20You'll%20get%20more%20coverage%20from%20Silk%20%26amp%3B%20Snow%2C%20but%20the%20Bearaby%20blanket%20is%20more%20compact%20for%20tossing%20on%20the%20couch.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20personal%20throw%20sizes%2C%20Bearaby%20offers%20its%20blanket%20in%20queen%20and%20king%20sizes%20too%2C%20which%20weigh%20in%20at%2020%20and%2025%20pounds%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%20of%20note%2C%20Bearaby's%20Cotton%20Napper%20is%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglobal-standard.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGOTS%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A