%3BWhether%20it's%20an%20essay%20or%20an%20oral%20exam%20or%20anything%20else%20%E2%80%94%20you're%20going%20to%20go%20in%20and%20the%20AI%20examiner%20is%20going%20to%20be%20with%20you%20doing%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoffman%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20actually%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20that%20will%20be%20harder%20to%20fake%20than%20the%20pre-AI%20times.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20the%20advent%20of%20AI%2C%20Hoffman%20said%2C%20ways%20to%20%26quot%3Bhack%26quot%3B%20the%20educational%20system%20already%20existed%2C%20such%20as%20piling%20on%20just%20enough%20knowledge%20to%20pass%20a%20written%20test%20or%20rushing%20to%20complete%20a%20passable%20essay%20that%20didn't%20dive%20much%20deeper%20than%20surface%20level.%20Potential%20AI%20examiners%20aside%2C%20Hoffman%20suggests%20that%20assessments%20like%20oral%20tests%2C%20which%20he%20believes%20are%20more%20difficult%20than%20written%2C%20could%20force%20students%20to%20study%20more%20intensely%20and%20absorb%20more%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPart%20of%20the%20reason%20why%20oral%20exams%20are%20hard%20%E2%80%94%20generally%20reserved%20for%20Ph.D.%20students%2C%20sometimes%20master's%20students%2C%20et%20cetera%20%E2%80%94%20is%20because%20actually%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20oral%20exams%2C%20you%20got%20to%20be%20across%20the%20whole%20zoom%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoffman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20let's%20think%20if%20every%20class%20had%20an%20oral%20exam%20essentially%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BOoh%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20learn%20a%20whole%20lot%20more%20in%20order%20to%20do%20this.%20And%20I%20think%20that's%20ultimately%20how%20this%20stuff%20will%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20less%20drastic%20ways%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-in-the-classroom-has-some-people-worried-teachers-arent-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eteachers%20could%20be%20using%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20their%20advantage%2C%20Hoffman%20added%2C%20that%20don't%20require%20them%20to%20entirely%20rewrite%20their%20curriculums.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20they%20believe%20that%20AI%20essays%20are%20subpar%2C%20they%20can%20provide%20students%20with%20examples%20of%20what%20%3Cem%3Enot%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlright%2C%20so%20you're%20teaching%20a%20class%20on%20Jane%20Austen%20and%20her%20relevance%20to%2C%20call%20it%2C%20early%20literary%20criticism%2C%20or%20something%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20you%20say%2C%20'Okay%2C%20well%20I%20went%20to%20ChatGPT%20and%20I%20generated%2010%20essays%2C%20and%20here's%20the%2010.%20These%20are%20D%20minuses.%20Do%20better.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20important%20thing%2C%20Hoffman%20said%2C%20is%20that%20teachers%20bring%20AI%20into%20the%20classroom%20in%20some%20way%2C%20big%20or%20small%2C%20if%20only%20to%20gain%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20how%20it%20can%20be%20applied%20in%20their%20fields.%20No%20matter%20their%20focus%20areas%2C%20it%20would%20be%20to%20their%20%E2%80%94%20and%20their%20students'%20%E2%80%94%20detriment%20to%20%26quot%3Bignore%20the%20new%20tool%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20a%20disruptive%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoffman%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20bunch%20of%20professors%2C%20just%20like%20classic%2C%20established%20professionals%20who%20go%2C%20'I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20disrupted.%20I%20want%20to%20keep%20my%20curriculum%20the%20way%20it%20is.%20I%20want%20to%20keep%20doing%20the%20thing%20that%20I'm%20doing.'%20And%20it's%20like%2C%20'Well%2C%20no%2C%20you%20can't%2C'%20right%3F%20And%20so%20you%20need%20to%20be%20learning%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoffman%2C%20who%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20further%20comment%20on%20the%20topic%2C%20argues%20it's%20now%20an%20educator's%20responsibility%20to%20get%20their%20students%20ready%20to%20work%20with%20AI%2C%20given%20that%20he%20believes%20it%20will%20transform%20their%20future%20workplaces%2C%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20central%20thing%20is%20preparing%20students%20to%20be%20capable%2C%20healthy%2C%20happy%20participants%20in%20the%20new%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20obviously%20your%20ability%20to%20engage%20with%2C%20deploy%2C%20leverage%2C%20utilize%2C%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20AI%20agents%2C%20et%20cetera%20%E2%80%94%20is%20going%20to%20be%20absolutely%20essential.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20teacher%20changing%20your%20approach%20to%20assignments%20or%20exams%20in%20the%20age%20of%20ChatGPT%3F%20Contact%20the%20author%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Asperkel%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Esperkel%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-reid-hoffman-ai-education-college-exams-harder-cheat-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747332598000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680ca7593fe8d39283642cc3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-reid-hoffman-ai-education-college-exams-harder-cheat-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20AI%20cheating%20rises%2C%20Reid%20Hoffman%20expects%20teachers%20to%20turn%20to%20tests%20such%20as%20oral%20exams%20that%20force%20students%20to%20understand%20a%20subject%20more%20deeply.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sperkel%40insider.com%20(Sarah%20Perkel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A244%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-reid-hoffman-ai-education-college-exams-harder-cheat-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian-origin%20politicians%20push%20for%20domestic%20H-1B%20visa%20renewal%2C%20major%20MAGA%20row%20triggered%22%2C