0series%20on%20innovations%20in%20logistics.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Hurricane%20Helene%20hit%20North%20Carolina%20in%20late%20September%2C%20it%20caused%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.osbm.nc.gov%2Fhurricane-helene-dna%2Fopen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2459%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20damages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20businesses%20damaged%20was%20one%20of%20the%20US's%20main%20manufacturers%20of%20IV%20fluids%2C%20used%20to%20rehydrate%20patients%20and%20give%20them%20medicine.%20The%20resultant%20shortage%20forced%20hospitals%20to%20conserve%20and%20reduce%20their%20use%20of%20IV%20fluids%2C%20which%20led%20to%20canceled%20surgeries%20and%20treatment%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20disruptions%20to%20hospital%20inventory%20have%20long%20been%20hard%20to%20predict%20and%20difficult%20for%20hospitals%20to%20navigate.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20keeping%20too%20much%20of%20a%20given%20item%20on%20hand%20is%20wasteful.%20In%202019%2C%20hospitals%20spent%20about%20%2425.7%20billion%20on%20supplies%20that%20they%20didn't%20need%2C%20the%20consulting%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fguidehouse.com%2F-%2Fmedia%2Fwww%2Fsite%2Finsights%2Fhealthcare%2F2022%2Fdownloads%2Fnavigant-supply-chain-2019-infog.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENavigant%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20in%20a%20study%20of%20over%202%2C100%20hospitals%20%E2%80%94%20about%20%2412.1%20million%20for%20an%20average%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20reduce%20waste%2C%20while%20ensuring%20providers%20have%20the%20medical%20supplies%20they%20need%2C%20some%20leading%20hospital%20systems%20are%20using%20automation%2C%20predictive%20analytics%2C%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20manage%20inventory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20asked%20supply%20chain%20managers%20from%20three%20systems%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Cleveland%20Clinic%2C%20the%20Mayo%20Clinic%2C%20and%20Rush%20University%20Medical%20Center%20%E2%80%94%20about%20how%20they%20use%20machine%20learning%2C%20generative%20AI%2C%20sensors%2C%20and%20robotics%20to%20anticipate%20shortages%20and%20help%20with%20contracting%20and%20ordering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBusiness%20Insider%3A%20What%20are%20some%20of%20the%20most%20effective%20and%20innovative%20ways%20that%20you're%20making%20use%20of%20AI%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20Dudas%2C%20Mayo%20Clinic's%20division%20chair%20of%20supply%20chain%20strategy%3A%20We've%20deployed%20autonomous%20delivery%20and%20robotic%20warehouse%20fulfilment%20%E2%80%94%20robots%20that%20pick%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20advancing%20our%20algorithms%20for%20auto-replenishment%20to%20be%20even%20more%20accurate.%20We're%20also%20using%20AI%20to%20explore%20savings%20opportunities%20and%20understand%20the%20sustainability%20of%20those%20opportunities%20over%20the%20length%20of%20an%20agreement%2C%20based%2C%20for%20example%2C%20on%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20doing%20advanced%20analytics%20in%20high-spend%20categories%20%E2%80%94%20we're%20just%20getting%20a%20lot%20smarter%20about%20what's%20happening%20with%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20precision.%20Even%20our%20expense%20management%2C%20we're%20looking%20at%20profit%20and%20loss%2C%20and%20supply%20expense%2C%20to%20understand%20what's%20happening%20from%20a%20budgetary%20perspective.%20Based%20on%20the%20present%20and%20what's%20happened%20in%20the%20past%2C%20we%20can%20look%20forward%20with%20some%20degree%20of%20accuracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeoff%20Gates%2C%20Cleveland%20Clinic's%20senior%20director%20of%20supply%20chain%20management%3A%20In%20some%20of%20our%20tools%2C%20instead%20of%20having%20someone%20click%20lots%20of%20buttons%20and%20type%20data%20into%2020%20or%20more%20fields%2C%20for%20example%2C%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20automate%20that%20process%20with%20AI%2C%20which%20saves%20employees%2020%20minutes%20every%20time.%20Those%20are%20the%20tasks%20that%20are%20the%20biggest%20benefit%20from%20a%20pure%20efficiency%20standpoint%20%E2%80%94%20they%20let%20people%20focus%20on%20other%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20use%20AI%20for%20document%20recognition%20and%20have%20been%20using%20it%20to%20manage%20invoices%20through%20our%20ERP%20inventory-management%20system%20for%20the%20last%20four%20years.%20If%20a%20medical-supply%20rep%20has%20a%20bill%20sheet%20that%20needs%20to%20get%20processed%20%E2%80%94%20to%20create%20a%20purchase%20order%20%E2%80%94%20the%20rep%20submits%20it%2C%20and%20our%20tool%20automatically%20creates%20a%20requisition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20distribution%2C%20our%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20a%20better%20view%20of%20what%20we%20have%20within%20our%20health%20system%20and%20the%20hospital.%20Our%20goal%20with%20key%20suppliers%20is%20to%20be%20able%20to%20see%20which%20supplies%20they%20have%20in%20their%20warehouses%20and%20to%20predict%20disruptions.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20we%20can%20see%20that%20a%20supplier%20doesn't%20have%20a%20shipment%20coming%20in%2C%20the%20system%20would%20alert%20us%20that%20we'll%20have%20a%20problem%20in%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeremy%20Strong%2C%20Rush%20University%20Medical%20Center's%20vice%20president%20of%20supply%20chain%3A%20For%20inventory%20management%2C%20we%20have%20weighted%20bin%20systems%20in%20all%20heavy-volume%20areas.%20When%20a%20nurse%20takes%20something%20out%20and%20puts%20something%20back%20in%2C%20we%20know%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20we%20implemented%20that%2C%20we%20could%20start%20to%20be%20proactive.%20We%20have%20a%20system%20that%20includes%20our%20distributor's%20data%20about%20inventory%20coming%20into%20their%20distribution%20center.%20They%20can%20see%20where%20our%20utilization%20patterns%20are%20changing.%20Then%20AI%20reviews%20all%20that.%20A%20back-order%20dashboard%20creates%20alerts%20when%20automatic%20supply-refill%20levels%20across%20the%20system%20are%20low%2C%20inventory%20is%20low%20at%20the%20distribution%20center%2C%20or%20shipments%20from%20manufacturers%20are%20taking%20longer%20than%20anticipated.%20We%20can%20anticipate%20that%20we're%20going%20to%20run%20out%20in%20a%20week%20from%20now%20or%20going%20to%20have%20a%20back-order%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20use%20it%20in%20contract%20management.%20When%20a%20contract%20is%20loaded%20in%2C%20AI%20will%20send%20it%20to%20the%20category%20manager%20with%20a%20summary%20and%20potential%20clauses%20to%20review.%20It%20can%20also%20automatically%20send%20contracts%20to%20the%20cybersecurity%20team%20for%20approval.%20If%20it%20has%20patient%20information%2C%20it%20sends%20it%20to%20the%20risk%20lawyers.%20If%20it%20has%20indemnification%2C%20it%20sends%20it%20to%20our%20regular%20lawyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20some%20of%20the%20advantages%20of%20automation%20that%20your%20system%20has%20realized%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDudas%3A%20Our%20automation%20gives%20us%20agility.%20We%20can%20see%20things%20sooner%20and%20adjust%20faster%20because%20of%20our%20technology%20but%20also%20because%20of%20our%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomebody%20asked%20me%20the%20other%20day%2C%20%26quot%3BWhere%20are%20you%20advancing%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20advancing.%20We're%20keeping%20up%20with%20all%20of%20the%20curveballs%20we%20get%20thrown%20on%20a%20day-to-day%20basis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGates%3A%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAt%20this%20point%2C%20the%20tools%20have%20touched%20almost%20everyone%20in%20the%20supply%20chain.%20Even%20a%20specific%20process%20that%20only%20impacts%20one%20or%20two%20people%20who%20were%20doing%20those%20tasks%20allows%20us%20to%20be%20more%20efficient%20and%20accurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrong%3A%20The%20goal%20was%20to%20move%20from%20being%20reactive%20and%20putting%20out%20fires%20to%20being%20more%20predictive%2C%20to%20prevent%20fires%20from%20happening%2C%20see%20things%20ahead%20of%20time%2C%20and%20be%20more%20efficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20also%20sped%20up%20contract%20review.%20We%20cut%20the%20time%20it%20takes%20to%20review%20them%20in%20half%20and%20more%20than%20doubled%20the%20number%20of%20reviews%20each%20contract%20gets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20advice%20do%20you%20have%20for%20other%20companies%20interested%20in%20implementing%20AI%20to%20streamline%20inventory%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDudas%3A%20Recognize%20that%20you%20can't%20do%20everything%20yourself.%20Even%20as%20big%20as%20our%20organization%20is%2C%20it's%20not%20big%20enough.%20Scale%20is%20your%20friend%20in%20the%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGates%3A%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESome%20things%20weren't%20necessarily%20the%20biggest%20opportunities%20to%20start%20with%2C%20but%20they%20were%20low-risk%20processes%20that%20gave%20us%20the%20skillset%20needed%20to%20leverage%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20most%20focused%20on%20finding%20the%20right%20solution%20for%20the%20problem%20rather%20than%20forcing%20a%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrong%3A%20The%20best%20tasks%20or%20processes%20to%20tackle%20are%20ones%20that%20are%20repetitive%20or%20require%20pulling%20and%20summarizing%20data%20from%20multiple%20digital%20sources.%20Tackle%20these%2C%20and%20you%20can%20gain%20efficiencies%2C%20improve%20productivity%2C%20and%20be%20proactive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-hospital-inventory-management-advice-mayo-clinic-cleveland-clinic-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747331071000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68250a5468a2929008015ab9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-hospit